Text.string: I like you when you're angry.
Give in to the bloodlust, beast!
Best to close your eyes. They like those.
Eat the tendons first, it's good for your beak!
See the skills of a true predator!
My hunt will not end here.
Why? Why did I decide to simulate pain?
I will hunt you all the way to hell.
Just a rest before the hunt continues.
I'll kill you! I'll kill all of you!
This is not the last of me.
Not yet. So many left to kill...
I am back to take your hides!
I will walk with Death, but not today.
Death is my friend. She can wait.
Ha! You fell for my ruse!
You should have finished me off.
No! I will not be put down!
Before it was the challenge. Now I'm angry!
What would I do without you, beast?
I definitely distracted them for you!
I hunt. I die. I hunt again.
That's it, I'm doubling my scalp quota.
I cut my way out of Hell and now I'm back.
My urge to kill has only grown.
Death sent me back. She is as cruel as she is beautiful.
For a moment, I knew peace. I'd like to avoid that in the future.
There is still much to hunt.
I smell blood on the wind.
Painful? Yes. Humbling? No. I'm still the best.
Quickly now, the hunt still rages.
I'm not mad. I just want to pull our enemy apart. Slowly.
I will call on you later.
Back to your burrow for now.
Go, boy. I will call on you later.
Run free until I call upon you.
Go on, boy. Be off for now.
I will call on you soon, little friend.
Take your mischief elsewhere for now.
I have need of you, beast!
Good to see you, my boy!
You really wanted that one, eh?
Who's my little predator? You are.
You're getting good at this, beast!
Hard of shell and quick of claw!
Knew I could count on you, girl!
I send you all to Death!
Weak! All of you are weak!
The hunt is not the only way to prove myself.
We must hunt as a pack, or be destroyed.
I am here to kill. I hope we share interests.
I never had a friend before. At least, not one with two legs.
How could I let this happen?
We will hunt together again soon.
Come here if you need a health kit.
I like the look of that.
This is no luck. The hunt is pleased with me.
Oh, the things I could kill with this...
I'm getting antsy. The hunt is calling me!
The longer I stand here, the more likely something is hunting me.
How can I follow the hunt by not moving?
Boring. I wish I'd kept some bones to whittle.
The hunt gnaws at the back of my mind. It's quite pleasant.
I've heard humans in this situation sometimes hum to themselves. A flaw in their biology, clearly.
I have no heart to give to Death. Perhaps if I collected other people's hearts... yes, a thousand should do it.
A human would be pondering the meaning of life right now. Let me try. [SFX: ping] Oh, there it is. Makes sense, I guess.
Just admiring the scenery. Imagining it drenched in blood.
I am not “zoning out”. I am lying in wait.
Give me new strength, shiny box!
Let's see, let's see. What'll we have this time, eh?
It's Eridian script, but my database is strangely empty.
This writing is familiar, but I cannot understand.
Could that be... no. No, I'm imagining things.
Now I see the truth of things.
Let me see what lies within.
I believe I can break this now.
What is the purpose of this thing?
I believe I can bring this to life now.
I must know this relic's purpose.
I can now unlock this relic's secret.
It doesn't capture my hunter's soul... but it's good enough for social media.
All right, I admit it. I look good.
Is this what they call a “selfish”?
Did you do that for “the gram”? Who is this “Gram”?
My skills need sharpening. You will be my whetstone.
This is teambuilding. I don't trust anyone who can't kill me.
The hunt can teach us both!
Of course. Are we playing for skins?
Ahhh, a test of skill, is it?
Bloodsport? I knew I liked you.
I submit. You are a true hunter.
I will be faster next time. Sharper.
Oof. You have my respect, packmate.
I'm fine, I'm just... inspecting these tracks. Yes.
Take this not as a loss, but as a lesson.
Feed now, beast! (beat) Just kidding, just kidding. Ha!
I... am in need of... assistance...
I am not ready for Death!
I have so much fight left in me!
There's no shame in asking for help!
Thank you. Would you like some trash from my pockets?
Thank you. I was not ready to meet Death.
We hunt better as a pack.
That's why I keep you around!
Knew I could count on you.
That's... one way to do it.
Surely there are more pleasant methods.
That was unpleasant, but thank you anyway.
I'm up, I'm up. Thank you.
Let's get back to it, girl!
I'm all better now, thank you.
Take my hand, and be renewed.
Your hunt is not yet over.
This is why I travel alone.
The pack leaves no one behind.
Fear not, I've seen worse. Only barely, though.
From what I understand of blood, you're doing it wrong.
Let me know if you die, and I'll just turn this into a corpse frisk.
I'll not let Death take you. She is mine.
Come back. We are stronger together.
You are predator, not prey. On your feet!
It's okay, I can fix it.
I will expect better next time.
Someone got the better of you, eh?
I've got you, I've got you.
A chest! The hunt rewards us.
You are reckless! And I love it!
I'm done driving. You take it.
Want a spin at the wheel?
These things are weapons in the right hands.
I love the sound of crashing metal!
Come, friend. They will not hunt themselves.
Did I save your life? Yes. Did I inspect you for weak points? We may never know.
Glad to see the life back in you!
You have fight in you yet!
There is more to do, my friend.
We have much ahead of us.
Go now, with fury in your heart!
Go and take some new bones.
Good. Now find yourself a chewtoy.
There, there. You're all better now.
Back to the hunt with you!
Ready to get back to the fight?
You're good for another round. Let's go!
We may want to bail out.
I am many things, but flameproof is not one of them. Yet.
Flames are never a good sign.
Perhaps it is time to abandon ship?
Would it be wise to walk now?
I... think we ought to walk.
We should get out of here!
Think of all the scalps I can hold now!
I admit, aesthetics are indeed important.
Even I enjoy a change from time to time.
Look upon me, for I am beauteous.
That will look excellent with blood on it!
If Death could see me now...
A hunter is only as good as their armory.
How do I want to kill today?
What would kill the most things?
My keen sense of direction is pointing me... where, exactly?
Where will the hunt take me next?
Self-improvement is the only way to survive.
What will best serve the hunt?
And a good deal was had by all.
If you cheated me, I will hunt you down.
Let us do it again some time.
I understand now. You are not done with me yet.
I hear her voice. She is calling me home.
The hunt claims all, in time.
I must... save... [different voice] Backup complete.
Damn... I have more to do. All is not yet forgiven.
My charge is not yet complete. They await my return.
Could I ever have finished my hunt? Was it ever real?
I will rise again. I will hunt once more. I am FL4K.
The hunt has more to teach me.
Will this be it? Will I meet Death?
Don't roll in -- he's rolling in it.
You want to go on a hunt?
What's that? Do you smell some prey?
Look at that little butt waggle.
You want to hear a good joke?
I've never had an itch, so I can't judge.
Do what you have to do.
All those manners classes and this is how you do me.
So, you've found me some loot?
You've got a nose for treasure, I see.
Knew there was a reason I kept you around.
Don't pee on it this time.
Ah, you find something for me?
Let's see if my knife fits in your skull.
I want to see what your guts look like.
You're already dead. You know that, right?
A badass! A chance to learn something new.
Badass or not, you will die!
Another alpha! There can only be one.
You will make a fine gift for Death.
You look like a trophy kill.
Are you a predator, or is that just a costume?
You there, how are your last breaths going?
Prove yourself once again, little friend!
Are you ready to hunt, little friend?
Come, little friend. Time for a fight!
I will put this to good use.
This metal beast is now mine.
We make a good hunting party.
Best to avoid a Siren's grasp. For next time.
What did you call that last time? An “alleyed oop”?
I should have packed more grenades.
I must have thrown them all.
The hunt requires a pack. Time to choose.
I don't know how to do that yet.
I must improve before I can do that.
A skill I have yet to learn.
This is beyond my current abilities.
I must hone myself sharper to use this.
It is beyond my considerable skill.
I have work to do before I can use that.
I must work harder before I can use this.
I am not yet ready for this.
I shouldn't get rid of this yet.
This is still of some use to me.
I know only the eternal hunt.
I am a knife that only grows sharper.
Climbing ever higher over the bones of my enemies.
I live only for Death and her glorious hunt!
So many kills behind me. So many ahead.
This is why my credit is terrible.
I have no blood, so I'm taking yours.
Let the life bleed from you!
Some days you hunt, some days you are hunted.
The hunt continues. But yours won't.
Pathetic end for a pathetic creature.
You are prey. This is the way of things.
Fall, and be reborn to the hunt!
Death is natural, but yours was thrilling!
Death is beautiful... most of the time.
Killing is an art. That was a splatter painting.
Ahaha, I wash in your blood!
I love the sound of bones breaking!
I hope this jacket is stainproof.
The weak fall to the strong.
You are insignificant. And weak. And no one will mourn you.
You were dead the moment we crossed paths.
I am predator, you are prey!
I felt your end. I felt it.
This was all worth it, just to kill you.
May we meet again... on the hunt.
I send you to Death. She will appreciate you.
Pride goeth before shitting the bed.
Under all that brawn, you were still prey.
You should have run. Not that it would have mattered.
I wish I could kill you all over again.
